data.description: Modernly Style Home! This one of a kind home has been updated with a beautiful white cabinet kitchen and granite countertops. The family room is the perfect space for gatherings, the beautiful beamed ceiling gives a grand feel. The family room also features a fireplace to cozy up in the winter months. There are 2 spacious bedrooms as well as another room that could be a 3rd bedroom. Both restooms offer a tranquil feel with updated countertops with one featuring a walk-in shower while the other offers a tub shower. This home is perfect for someone looking for a starter home, downsizing, or build their investment portfolio. Located near schools, shopping, and short distance to highway 43!
